<HEAD>CBS Names NBC Producer Washington Bureau Chief</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Barbara Cohen, executive producer of NBC's ``Meet
the Press'' program since 1985, has been named CBS News vice
president and Washington bureau chief.
   Cohen, 43, has been with NBC News since 1983, when she was named
