<HEAD>Shultz Huddles With Deputy Foreign Minister</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Israeli Deputy Foreign Minister Benjamin
Netanyahu held what he called ``a very good conversation'' Thursday
with Secretary of State George P. Shultz amid indications Israel
will soon unveil a new plan for settling its conflict with the Arabs.
   Netanyahu declined to say after the 40-minute session whether he
